      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, preserved in a state that mirrors its original showroom delivery. Every surface, mechanical component, and electronic system functions with absolute precision, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark in automotive excellence.",
