    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it\u2019s always been kept in a climate-controlled garage. It looks and smells brand new, with not a single scratch or scuff in sight. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
